To our subscribers

The Union Leaders offices at 100 William Loeb Drive will be closed to customers for the rest of July as we relocate some of our operations. Customer service associates will continue to be available at 603-668-1210, Monday through Friday, 7 a.m. to 4:45 p.m., and Saturday, 6 to 11 a.m.

The circulation department may be reached by email at subscriptions@unionleader.com. The customer service department will reopen in August in a location to be announced soon.
